question: Hō͘ sèng-hêng 'Kông-li̍t jī-chiòng' ê hō͘-chúi, siáⁿ chi̍t ê hō͘-chúi ū sió-khuán ê tiong-sim ap-le̍k, piáⁿ-chòe hit kuńg siōng tōa ê kiông-le̍k?
Nāi-suànn 'Ivan' kap 'Jokwe' ê 'Refs' ê sò͘-jī-luî piáu-sī sí-lâng-sò͘, siáⁿ-chē lâng sí tī kó͘-chhoân chiong Maradagascar chhit-tó ê sî?
Tī só͘-ū sǹg-chò 'Chhiông-le̍k jia̍t-tāi hong-pò' ê hong-thai tang-tiong, ūi-chāi chòe-tn̂g sî-kan ê hong-thai tùi khai-sí ji̍t kàu kiat-sū ji̍t?

Koa tioh, tui 'Phik kip ki̍p-tō͘' lâi kóng, tùi chheⁿ-kùi bóe (Sibat goe̍h) kàu āu-kî ê goe̍h-hun (Ngo̍at goe̍h - Chhit goe̍h), siâⁿ-chúi ê ki̍p-tō͘ ê piau-chún chhoán-tōaⁿ sī chūi-chūi? (Iûⁿ chhiúⁿ tui 'Phik kip ki̍p-tō͘' lâi kóng, tùi chheⁿ-kùi bóe (Sibat goe̍h) kàu āu-kî ê goe̍h-hun (Ngo̍at goe̍h - Chhit goe̍h), siâⁿ-chúi ê ki̍p-tō͘ ê piau-chún chhoán-tōaⁿ sī chūi-chūi?)
answer: Chiuⁿ-kù chìn-tiâu chhāi-bīn, chheⁿ-kùi chìn-chêng ê sî-chūn, siâⁿ-chúi ê ki̍p-tō͘ sī ti̍t-chiap chiūⁿ-thiⁿ ê. Sibat goe̍h, chheⁿ-kùi chho͘-chho͘ khai-sí ê sî-chūn, lóng sī bô chin ki̍p-tō͘ ê hē-thóng, pí-lūn chū 'Jia̍t-tō͘ chin-tō͘-chiah' ê. Āu-lâi sī 'Kó͘-tō͘ jia̍t-tō͘-chúi' kap 'Tiong-tō͘ jia̍t-tō͘-chúi', kàu Chhit goe̍h. Chiah-ê lóng sī siâⁿ-chúi tōa thiⁿ ê chêng-kí. Chóng-sī, tùi It goe̍h bóe kàu Sam goe̍h, siâⁿ-chúi ê ki̍p-tō͘ chiâⁿ bē-khah ki̍p-tō͘. Chiah-ê sî-chūn, tō ū chin ki̍p-tō͘ ê 'Jia̍t-tō͘ tōa-chúi' kap 'Kó͘-tō͘ jia̍t-tō͘ tōa-chúi'.

question: Thak chi̍t-ê la̍k-seng ê hong-pau miâ, i tī-koaⁿ February thiⁿ tō oa̍h-lo̍h, koh chin tiōng-iàu ê kip-pia̍t sī 'Intensetropicalcyclone'?
Tī chit ê phiau chiong ê te̍k-sù sū-kiāⁿ lāi-bīn, ū kúi-á phah-sǹg sī hō͘ sǹg chòe "jia̍t-tāi hong-bão" (chēmn̄g-kè jia̍t-tāi hong-bão, tiong-téng jia̍t-tāi hong-bão)?
Nāi kám-chió 5 hPa, chin-sī tē-sìng tòng-chok ê sî, it-che̍k ê 'Moderatetropicalstorm' sū-kiāⁿ ê pêng-kun hā-tōa-chù sī siáⁿ-chōe?
Tōa-sîng-pō͘ ê hong-sok kap tiong-sim ap-le̍k ê koan-hē tī bô-kâng ê tōa-chhoán hun-lūi lāi-bīn chhim-tō͘ ê koan-hē chóaⁿ-iâⁿ.
answer: Hong-sok kap tiong-sim ap-le̍k chi kan ū chi̍t ê kiông-kó͘ ê tò-tóe koan-hē. Chiàⁿ-chāi, chóaⁿ-iâⁿ ê tōa-sîng-pō͘ ê hun-lūi ke-chiap kiông-tōa (chhiūⁿ, tùi 'jia̍t-tāi thiah-tōa-chhoán' kàu 'kiông-kiet jia̍t-tāi tōa-chhoán'), hong-sok ê sò͘-ta̍t chiân-tîⁿ sêng-tiông, chiâm tiong-sim ap-le̍k ê sò͘-ta̍t chiân-tîⁿ kiám-sut. Chhiūⁿ-chāi, 'jia̍t-tāi thiah-tōa-chhoán' 07 ê hong-sok sī 35 km/h kap ap-le̍k 1003 hPa, tān-sī 'kiông-kiet jia̍t-tāi tōa-chhoán' Hondo ê hong-sok sī 215 km/h kap ap-le̍k 915 hPa.

question: U cap-kah khah chē ê hêng, chhin-chhiūⁿ Fame kap Ivan ê sèng-miâ, lóng-chóng ū chu-liāu chha-khoeh, tùi chu-liāu ê siau-chū tō chhiuⁿ m̄-tio̍h. Chīn-pún ê chhiong-pò, chhiuⁿ Damage (USD) kap Deaths nn̄g khoân ê chu-liāu bô chèng-tòe ê hong-sek, cháiⁿ-iáⁿ kā chit ê khah-chū-ê hong-sek chīn chhut-lâi.
answer: Chit lūi ê chong hō͘ sèng-miâ ê Damage (USD) kap Deaths só͘ ū ê chu-liāu, lóng ū chi̍t khoán tòe ê chu-liāu ji̍p-khì ê chhò-gō͘. Damage (USD) khoân ê chu-liāu sī si̍t-chè téng ê ji̍t-kî (chhin-chhiūⁿ January27, February17). Deaths khoân ê chu-liāu sī hō͘ teh chong ê hong-só͘ hong-le̍k ê chu-liāu. Si̍t-chè ê sí-jîn-sò͘, nā ū ê, chhiuⁿ tòe teh Refs khoân ê lāi-bīn.

question: Tī chit ê chu-liāu tiong, ū hông-lêng ê hong-sok sī chin iau-bīt, pí kî-thaⁿ ê hông-lêng lóng koân chin chē?
Koh tua-liat ê hong-pau sia̍p 185 km/h ê sok-tō͘ ū?
